beer.beer_description:
MOSAIC / SIMCOE / CHINOOK

Fly the coop is a big old hazy DIPA bursting with juicy tropical flavour. We decided to focus on some of our favourite heavy hitting US hops which have melded perfectly with the expensive Sherlock yeast strain from Mogwai Labs.
beer.beer_style: IPA - Imperial / Double New England / Hazy
